1. What is your favourite season?
2. I like summer/winter/spring/autumn.
3. In the summer/winter/spring/autumn...
4. We go to the seaside.
5. I prefer autumn. 
6. Peaceful and quiet.
7. You can ski in winter.
8. Permit me... 
9. Spring is when nature wakes up and everything
   comes to life again.

